# sfjc.dev owner sync

- UI: **sync password** (never "sync key" in user-facing copy)
- Owner sync password user id: `MLpnko#12` (see `docs/SFJC-ADMIN.md`)
- Server env: `SFJC_SYNC_PASSWORD` — required in production for Notes AI
- Admin device UUIDs: `src/data/sfjc-admin-devices.ts` (iPhone, Macbook Air, Work Laptop)
- Notes AI (`/api/notes/lookup`, `/api/notes/embed`): gated by sync password when env is set
- localStorage keys stay `notes_sync_key` / `daily_learn_sync_key` for backward compatibility

When adding owner-only features, prefer validating sync password server-side and referencing admin device ids from `sfjc-admin-devices.ts`.
